Package: ttrssR
Type: Package
Title: News Collection and Thematic Categorization via TT-RSS API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "Name", , "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Collects news articles from a Tiny Tiny RSS (TT-RSS) instance via
    its JSON API, normalizes them into a unified data frame, performs thematic
    classification using LDA, K-Means, or Yandex GPT in closed-set mode,
    stores results in ClickHouse, and exposes an interactive Shiny dashboard
    and an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server that serves classified data for
    AI-agent queries.
